tyle=\"font-size: 12px\">华硕 EAH6670/DI/1GD3 冰翼版</font></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; color: rgb(64,64,64); font-size: 14px; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; color: rgb(64,64,64); font-size: 14px; padding-top: 0px\">　　做工方面，华硕 EAH6670/DI/1GD3 冰翼版采用采用红色非公版PCB设计，供电方面显示核心与显存采用分离式供电设计，用料上搭配全固态优质电容与华硕独家S.A.P超合金电感，为显卡长期稳定运行提供强有力的保障。</p>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; color: rgb(64,64,64); font-size: 14px\" align=\"center\">\r\n<div align=\"center\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"显卡供电\" align=\"middle\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" style=\"border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-left: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; margin: 4px; vertical-align: top; border-top: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid\" src=\"http://i5.hexunimg.cn/2011-09-21/133565798.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><font style=\"font-size: 12px\">显卡供电</font></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; color: rgb(64,64,64); font-size: 14px; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; color: rgb(64,64,64); font-size: 14px; padding-top: 0px\">　　显存方面，华硕 EAH6670/DI/1GD3 冰翼版搭载了GDDR3显存颗粒，组成了1024MB/128bit的显存规格，默认核心显存频率分别是800MHz/1800MHz。</p>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; color: rgb(64,64,64); font-size: 14px\" align=