product/monitors/2013/LS23C570HS-XF/features/LS23C570HS-XF-45-0.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 13px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); line-height: 18px; padding-top: 0px\">三星显示器拥有极富创意的独特纤薄外观，现代感十足的透明颈和方形底座设计完美契合，方便实用，超薄屏幕在展现时尚风格的同时又不失强大的技术性能。三星灵感，点亮生活！</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; float: left; padding-bottom: 56px; margin: 0px; width: 420px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 15px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(101,79,61); line-height: 17px; padding-top: 0px; word-wrap: break-word\">灵晰高清 画质升级</h2>\r\n<img title=\"title\" alt=\"alt\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-top: 0px; vertical-align: middle; border-left: 0px; border-bottom: 0px\" src=\"http://www.samsung.com/cn/consumer-images/product/monitors/2013/LS23C570HS-XF/features/LS23C570HS-XF-59-1.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 13px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); line-height: 18px; padding-top: 0px\">灵晰高清功能可以直接对图片进行专业处理，增强图像品质，避免因放大操作而造成的图像品质下降的问题，同时在笔记本双屏显示处理时，色彩更加鲜活、艳丽，让您获得更加清晰、明锐的画面。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; float: left; padding-bottom: 56px; margin: 0px; width: 420px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 15px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(101,79,61); line-height: 17px; padding-top: 0px; word-wrap: break-word\">完美兼容Windows 8</h2>\r\n<img title=\"title\" alt=\"alt\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-top: 0px; vertical-align: middle; border-left: 0px; border-bottom: 0px\" src=\"http://www.samsung.com/cn/consumer-images/product/monitors/2013/LS23C570HS-XF/features/LS23C570HS-XF-52-0.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 13px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51)