INSERT INTO necs_goods VALUES('1026','214','DT001026','三星4021一体机','+','220','0','','9999','0.000','1100.00','1100.00','0.00','0','0','1','','','<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large\"><font size=\"6\">技术支持 同类产品咨询 售后服务与指导 </font></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large\"><font size=\"6\">138-0401-4325</font></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 45px; color: rgb(0,0,0); line-height: 18px; padding-top: 25px; font-family: microsoft yahei 微软雅黑 simsun arial sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word\">三星SCX-4021S将成本节省和优秀性能完美结合，设计紧凑时尚，这款多功能一体机让您的成本管理变得更加轻松简便，有效降低您的预算。它还具备诸多人性化设计，机器整体简单易用。</p>\r\n<div style=\"clear: both; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-size: 12px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow: hidden; width: 920px; color: rgb(0,0,0); line-height: normal; padding-top: 25px; font-family: microsoft yahei 微软雅黑 simsun arial sans-serif\">\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; float: left; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; width: 460px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; float: left; padding-bottom: 56px; margin: 0px; width: 420px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top: 0px; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(101,79,61); line-height: 17px; word-wrap: break-word\">灵活处理多重任务</h2>\r\n<img title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align: middle\" src=\"http://www.samsung.com/cn/consumer-images/product/printers-multifunction/2012/SCX-4021S-XIL/features/SCX-4021S-XIL-67-0.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 13px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); line-height: 18px; padding-top: 0px\">三星SCX-4021S 3合1多功能一体机，具有打印、复印、扫描功能，有效简化工作流程，保证办公打印操作能够尽可能地智能高效。SCX-4021S的高灵活性将有效消除您工作中遇到的障碍。一系列创新的智能运用，如身份证复印、N-Up打印/复印和扫描到电子邮件等，为您提供常用的必要功能。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; float: left; padding-bottom: 56px; margin: 0px; width: 420px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top: 0px; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(101,79,61); line-height: 17px; word-wrap: break-word\">强大处理器</h2>\r\n<img title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align: middle\" src=\"http://www.samsung.com/cn/consumer-images/product/printers-multifunction/2012/SCX-4021S-XIL/features/SCX-4021S-XIL-73-0.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 13px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); line-height: 18px; padding-top: 0px\">三星SCX-4021S，拥有433MHz处理器，可以满足您多种多样的文件处理要求，让您的工作更加轻松高效。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; float: left; padding-bottom: 56px; margin: 0px; width: 420px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top: 0px; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(101,79,61); line-height: 17px; word-wrap: break-word\">使用更少墨粉，减低更多成本</h2>\r\n<img title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align: middle\" src=\"http://www.samsung.com/cn/consumer-images/product/printers-multifunction/2012/SCX-4021S-XIL/features/SCX-4021S-XIL-43-0.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 13px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); line-height: 18px; padding-top: 0px\">三星多功能一体机的控制面板上设有&ldquo;环保&rdquo;按键，无需复杂的手动更改设置，一键点亮&ldquo;环保&rdquo;按键，您就能开启省墨模式，多合一打印，轻松完成墨粉、纸张和能耗的节省，让您用更少的墨粉打印每一页文件，还可以延长墨粉盒30%的使用寿命，更可大大降低您的每页打印成本。&ldquo;环保&rdquo;安监科随需要设置默认模式，为您提供最适合的经济环保打印服务。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; float: left; padding-bottom: 56px; margin: 0px; width: 420px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top: 0px; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(101,79,61); line-height: 17px; word-wrap: break-word\">节约成效清楚可见</h2>\r\n<img title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align: middle\" src=\"http://www.samsung.com/cn/consumer-images/product/printers-multifunction/2012/SCX-4021S-XIL/features/SCX-4021S-XIL-51-0.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 13px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); line-height: 18px; padding-top: 0px\">环保驱动还配备有环保效果模拟器，您每一次的打印设置后，都可以显示打印机根据您所选择的打印模式节省的二氧化碳排放、电耗、纸张用量、碳粉以及综合打印成本。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; float: left; padding-bottom: 56px; margin: 0px; width: 420px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top: 0px; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(101,79,61); line-height: 17px; word-wrap: break-word\">全面监控打印工作</h2>\r\n<img title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align: middle\" src=\"http://www.samsung.com/cn/consumer-images/product/printers-multifunction/2012/SCX-4021S-XIL/features/SCX-4021S-XIL-62-0.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 13px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); line-height: 18px; padding-top: 0px\">三星努力探索简化的打印管理。轻松打印管理能仅通过一个软件便为您全面监控打印机的各方面性能和状态。这意味着您决不会遇到打印时墨粉意外用完的情况，因为这款高效软件会帮您快速轻松地预定新的墨盒。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; float: left; padding-bottom: 56px; margin: 0px; width: 420px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top: 0px; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(101,79,61); line-height: 17px; word-wrap: break-word\">轻松快捷的身份证复印功能</h2>\r\n<img title=\"\" alt=\"\" data-ks-lazyload=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/tps/i4/T10B2IXb4cXXcHmcPq-85-85.gif\" style=\"vertical-align: middle\" src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/tps/i4/T10B2IXb4cXXcHmcPq-85-85.gif\" /><br />\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 13px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); line-height: 18px; padding-top: 0px\">特有的身份证复印功能能帮助您合并复印件，避免浪费时间和纸张。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; float: right; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; width: 460px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; float: left; padding-bottom: 56px; margin: 0px; width: 420px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top: 0px; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(101,79,61); line-height: 17px; word-wrap: break-word\">超大内存</h2>\r\n<img title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align: middle\" src=\"http://www.samsung.com/cn/consumer-images/product/printers-multifunction/2012/SCX-4021S-XIL/features/SCX-4021S-XIL-77-0.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 13px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); line-height: 18px; padding-top: 0px\">三星全新的升级版明星产品SCX-4021S，除了24PPM的超快打印速度外，还拥有64MB的超大内存，提高您的工作效率，除此之外，SCX-4021S的月打印负荷为12,000页，机器性能更加稳定。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; float: left; padding-bottom: 56px; margin: 0px; width: 420px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top: 0px; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(101,79,61); line-height: 17px; word-wrap: break-word\">大容量意味着更省钱</h2>\r\n<img title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align: middle\" src=\"http://www.samsung.com/cn/consumer-images/product/printers-multifunction/2012/SCX-4021S-XIL/features/SCX-4021S-XIL-69-0.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 13px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); line-height: 18px; padding-top: 0px\">三星使用价格合理高容量硒鼓，在进行打印时可以让您获得更低的每页打印成本。您会发现平均7个月才需要更换一次墨粉盒。此外，它的容量相比同等级竞品高20%，能够让您多打印将近400页文件。<br />\r\n<strong>*此机器可以通用SCX-4521F/4321的耗材SCX-4521D3</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; float: left; padding-bottom: 56px; margin: 0px; width: 420px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top: 0px; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(101,79,61); line-height: 17px; word-wrap: break-word\">轻松环保驱动，获取绝佳打印体验</h2>\r\n<img title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align: middle\" src=\"http://www.samsung.com/cn/consumer-images/product/printers-multifunction/2012/SCX-4021S-XIL/features/SCX-4021S-XIL-60-0.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 13px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); line-height: 18px; padding-top: 0px\">三星打印机内置的环保驱动功能让您每次都尽享物超所值的打印输出体验。使用这项有用的软件，您可以在打印前准确预览文件并根据需要进行调整。一键即可选择只打印文字或只打印图片，还能使用N-up多合一功能，打印2页或4页合一的文件，将墨粉用量减低20%。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; float: left; padding-bottom: 56px; margin: 0px; width: 420px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top: 0px; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(101,79,61); line-height: 17px; word-wrap: break-word\">可调节面板，简单易用</h2>\r\n<img title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align: middle\" src=\"http://www.samsung.com/cn/consumer-images/product/printers-multifunction/2012/SCX-4021S-XIL/features/SCX-4021S-XIL-86-0.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 13px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); line-height: 18px; padding-top: 0px\">可倾斜控制面板能调整至任何位置，让用户更方便使用。因此您可以选择舒适的方式操作和控制打印机。控制面板按键设计简单明了可以轻松完成所需操作。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; float: left; padding-bottom: 56px; margin: 0px; width: 420px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top: 0px; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(101,79,61); line-height: 17px; word-wrap: break-word\">屏幕打印 只需一键</h2>\r\n<img title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align: middle\" src=\"http://www.samsung.com/cn/consumer-images/product/printers-multifunction/2012/SCX-4021S-XIL/features/SCX-4021S-XIL-84-0.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 13px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); line-height: 18px; padding-top: 0px\">SCX-4021S的一键屏幕打印功能，无需额外编辑或剪切多余的网页文件内容，手指轻触即可完成打印。即使不在办公桌旁，您也可以轻松便利地打印屏幕上的所有内容。轻松打印，随时随地。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-right: 0px; background-position: 20px 10px; padding-left: 32px; font-size: 12px; background-attachment: scroll; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(136,13